The paper discusses deep learning methods for object detection and semantic segmentation in the context of autonomous driving, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses fusion methodologies and challenges, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on multi-modal perception, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
